  >
    Hola, soy José
  </h1>
  <p class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 max-sm:text-base">
    +2 años de experiencia. 
    <strong
      class="animate-text-gradient bg-gradient-to-r from-[#005f73] via-[#0a9396] to-[#005f73] dark:bg-gradient-to-r dark:from-[#bb3e03] dark:via-[#ca6702] dark:to-[#bb3e03] bg-[200%_auto] bg-clip-text text-xl text-transparent"
    >
      Desarrollador Web Frontend
    </strong> de Jujuy, Argentina.
  </p>
  <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-2 mt-4 md:mt-6">
    <a
      href="mailto:joariel17@gmail.com"
      id="gmail"
      onclick="copyMail()"
      class="flex gap-2 items-center py-2 px-4 text-sm font-semibold rounded-lg border bg-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-800 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 border-[#C5221F] hover:bg-[#C5221F]/20 dark:hover:bg-[#C5221F]/30 transition max-sm:text-xs max-sm:font-medium w-[92px] sm:w-[98px]"
    >
